                        <interp inst="t18490917-name-295" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM RANSLEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, S</hi> 61.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read Convicted July</hi> 1848, <hi rend="italic">and confined six month</hi>)—he is the person—this is the same coat he had on when I took him then. <hi rend="smallCaps">
